Overview

This dashboard shows Traffic overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested Traffic logs from Prisma Access.

It highlights the top actions performed by the firewall and identifies the top applications associated with network traffic. It visualizes traffic trends over time and provides detailed metrics such as source bytes, destination bytes, and total bytes transferred. The dashboard also lists the top security policy rules and provides insights into the primary reasons for session termination.
